<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563748>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. Ammothella symbia, UANL-FCB-PYCNO-0058, male: A, anterior end, frontal view; B, anterior end, showing chelifores; C, proboscis and palp, latero-frontal view; D, ocular tubercle, lateral view; E, complete specimen, dorsal view; F, complete specimen, posterior view; G, third leg; H, tarsus, propodus and claws of leg 3; I, oviger, proboscis and palp, ventral view; J, terminal articles of the oviger; K, abdomen, lateral view. Scale bars: K = 1 mm; A, G–I = 0.5 mm; C = 0.3 mm; B, D = 0.2 mm; E–F, H, I, J = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4563748/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563746>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. Ammothella symbia, UANL-FCB-PYCNO-0058, male: A, trunk, dorsal view; B, trunk, lateral view; C, palp; D, third leg; E, propodus; F, oviger. Scale bars: A–B, E = 0.5 mm; C–D, F = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4563746/files/figure.png" .

